1
00:01:19,400 --> 00:01:20,660
What are you looking at

2
00:01:20,840 --> 00:01:21,640
so intently?

3
00:01:23,520 --> 00:01:26,250
I'm looking at the water drops on this lotus leaf.

4
00:01:28,120 --> 00:01:28,600
Look.

5
00:01:29,280 --> 00:01:32,240
A small drop of water is a small world.

6
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:34,880
Many small drops gather together

7
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:36,720
to form a bigger world.

8
00:01:37,720 --> 00:01:39,000
These small water drops

9
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:40,560
are like knights,

10
00:01:41,320 --> 00:01:43,000
slowly gathering together.

11
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:44,160
Then,

12
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:45,460
they charge downward.

13
00:01:57,440 --> 00:01:58,440
I'm sorry.

14
00:01:59,240 --> 00:02:01,040
Am I acting a bit weird?

15
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:05,120
Actually,

16
00:02:05,960 --> 00:02:08,419
I usually don't notice these things either.

17
00:02:11,840 --> 00:02:13,700
I was often sick when I was little.

18
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:16,440
When I was getting an IV,

19
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:18,440
I had nothing else to do.

20
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:21,400
So I would lie in bed

21
00:02:21,720 --> 00:02:23,850
and watch the little drops from the IV.

22
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:26,520
Maybe since then,

23
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:28,680
I started observing things

24
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:30,610
that people don't usually notice.

25
00:02:32,200 --> 00:02:32,840
Like what?

26
00:02:39,920 --> 00:02:41,380
Like the clouds in the sky.

27
00:02:46,160 --> 00:02:48,800
I used to think clouds were only one color.

28
00:02:49,920 --> 00:02:51,560
Now, after observing,

29
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:53,880
I found they can be pink,

30
00:02:54,040 --> 00:02:54,800
yellow,

31
00:02:55,200 --> 00:02:55,960
purple,

32
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:59,280
and sometimes even black and gray.

33
00:03:00,440 --> 00:03:01,600
Different clouds

34
00:03:02,200 --> 00:03:03,640
have different stories.

35
00:03:07,480 --> 00:03:08,540
Look at that cloud.

36
00:03:13,480 --> 00:03:16,140
Doesn't it look like a mother dog with her puppy?

37
00:03:29,160 --> 00:03:30,240
And this awning.

38
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:33,680
Whenever the wind blows,

39
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:35,120
I feel like this awning

40
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:37,380
looks like many people dancing the hula.

41
00:03:45,040 --> 00:03:46,680
Am I being childish?

42
00:03:47,640 --> 00:03:48,240
No.

43
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:51,360
It's quite interesting.

44
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:54,079
Thank you.

45
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:18,600
You're back.

46
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:20,640
Cencen,

47
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:22,400
you're back.

48
00:04:24,520 --> 00:04:25,880
Mom, you scared me.

49
00:04:25,880 --> 00:04:28,560
Don't you recognize your mom just because of a facial mask?

50
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:29,800
Why did you come back so late?

51
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:31,600
You didn't answer your phone either.

52
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:33,800
I turned on Do Not Disturb during class,

53
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:35,440
and forgot to turn it off afterwards.

54
00:04:35,440 --> 00:04:37,560
What were you playing so late?

55
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:39,080
Just having dinner.

56
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:41,240
Eating dinner so late. This child.

57
00:04:41,760 --> 00:04:42,400
Xiaocen,

58
00:04:42,760 --> 00:04:45,020
come, let auntie put a facial mask on you.

59
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:46,760
No need, I'll go back first.

60
00:04:47,400 --> 00:04:47,960
Alright.

61
00:04:47,960 --> 00:04:48,680
Cencen,

62
00:04:49,400 --> 00:04:50,860
what did you forget again?

63
00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:52,960
I've heated this medicine for you twice.

64
00:04:52,960 --> 00:04:53,960
You're finally back.

65
00:04:53,960 --> 00:04:56,000
Mom, I know how to heat it myself.

66
00:04:59,840 --> 00:05:02,100
Sit there and finish it before you leave.

67
00:05:41,360 --> 00:05:42,200
Jingdezhen

68
00:05:42,760 --> 00:05:44,820
used to be the site of imperial kilns.

69
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:47,970
Only the most exquisite, top-quality porcelain

70
00:05:48,080 --> 00:05:49,680
would be selected and sent to the capital.

71
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:50,810
What about the rest?

72
00:05:52,159 --> 00:05:53,960
To prevent them from ending up among the common people,

73
00:05:53,960 --> 00:05:56,420
they were all smashed and buried on the spot.

74
00:05:56,520 --> 00:05:58,050
Therefore, in Jingdezhen,

75
00:05:58,680 --> 00:06:00,720
around many ancient kiln ruins,

76
00:06:01,400 --> 00:06:02,880
there are large amounts

77
00:06:03,200 --> 00:06:05,000
of ancient porcelain fragments

78
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:05,680
piled up.

79
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:09,040
Okay.

80
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:10,540
Please take a seat.

81
00:06:14,200 --> 00:06:15,200
In Jingdezhen,

82
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:17,680
the place where you encounter the most ancient porcelain

83
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:18,940
is the antique market.

84
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:21,720
It has official and folk kilns from past dynasties,

85
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:22,360
as well as

86
00:06:22,400 --> 00:06:25,660
different blue-and-white and famille-rose porcelains.

87
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:28,200
The antique market used to be called

88
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,160
the Ghost Market.

89
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:30,040
Ghost Market?

90
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:31,800
Is it haunted?

91
00:06:32,520 --> 00:06:33,450
The Ghost Market

92
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:35,840
was formed in the 1990s.

93
00:06:36,080 --> 00:06:37,960
It grew larger and larger.

94
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:40,800
At that time, every Monday,

95
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:42,200
it opened in the early morning.

96
00:06:42,200 --> 00:06:43,680
The items sold have unknown origins,

97
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:44,640
and they disperse at dawn.

98
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:45,159
So

99
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:46,560
it got the name

100
00:06:46,640 --> 00:06:47,440
Ghost Market.

101
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:49,120
Now these stalls

102
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:51,960
have all moved to the Sculpture Porcelain Factory.

103
00:06:51,960 --> 00:06:53,020
I'll take everyone

104
00:06:53,280 --> 00:06:54,800
to practice on site.

105
00:07:03,840 --> 00:07:04,370
How is it?

106
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:06,280
Is everyone here?

107
00:07:06,280 --> 00:07:06,960
Yes.

108
00:07:06,960 --> 00:07:07,440
We're here.

109
00:07:07,440 --> 00:07:09,200
This is the sculpture porcelain factory.

110
00:07:09,200 --> 00:07:11,640
Each of you has the task to choose a piece

111
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:14,520
of ancient porcelain from before the Republic of China.

112
00:07:14,520 --> 00:07:15,880
Will that be very expensive?

113
00:07:15,880 --> 00:07:16,520
Usually,

114
00:07:16,840 --> 00:07:18,800
you can get it for under 100 yuan.

115
00:07:19,200 --> 00:07:20,800
That seems affordable.

116
00:07:21,400 --> 00:07:22,560
Don't drop your guard.

117
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:24,800
Every stall owner here will say

118
00:07:24,960 --> 00:07:26,120
that the items at their stall

119
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:28,240
are genuine antiques.

120
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:29,240
However,

121
00:07:29,520 --> 00:07:31,840
there are many fakes mixed in.

122
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:32,760
This time,

123
00:07:32,880 --> 00:07:34,480
it's a test of your judgment.

124
00:07:34,760 --> 00:07:35,560
Are you ready?

125
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:36,450
Let's go.

126
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:37,360
Go.

127
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:38,490
Let's go take a look.

128
00:07:38,760 --> 00:07:39,800
Let's see who picks it first.

129
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:40,200
Let's go.

130
00:07:40,200 --> 00:07:40,560
Let's go together.

131
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:40,960
Go.

132
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:44,530
Yuexin, take a look at this.

133
00:07:56,200 --> 00:07:56,760
Mr. Yue,

134
00:07:57,200 --> 00:07:58,360
help me check this out.

135
00:07:58,360 --> 00:07:59,120
Is it real?

136
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:02,360
See for yourself.

137
00:08:04,080 --> 00:08:04,720
Come and see.

138
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:06,050
Pick whatever you like.

139
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:17,080
Handsome, come take a look.

140
00:08:17,080 --> 00:08:20,010
These are all Song Dynasty bluish-white porcelain.

141
00:08:22,200 --> 00:08:23,480
I like this one.

142
00:08:24,200 --> 00:08:25,560
Is this real?

143
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:44,000
Feel free to look around.

144
00:08:55,800 --> 00:08:56,400
Student.

145
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:58,880
Look at these blue and white porcelain shards.

146
00:08:58,880 --> 00:09:01,800
I have everything from the Yuan to Qing dynasties here.

147
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:03,130
Guaranteed authentic.

148
00:09:04,520 --> 00:09:06,400
How did you know I'm a student?

149
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:08,120
With my eyes,

150
00:09:08,400 --> 00:09:10,640
go ask around this ghost market.

151
00:09:15,560 --> 00:09:17,820
They are all very beautiful. Take a look.

152
00:09:22,400 --> 00:09:23,000
Miss.

153
00:09:23,120 --> 00:09:24,250
You have good taste.

154
00:09:25,160 --> 00:09:27,120
This is from the Qianlong reign,

155
00:09:27,520 --> 00:09:29,760
a conical bowl with pine, bamboo, and plum patterns.

156
00:09:29,760 --> 00:09:31,160
Absolutely a good stuff.

157
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:32,120
The style

158
00:09:32,640 --> 00:09:33,440
and the glaze.

159
00:09:35,360 --> 00:09:36,720
When it comes to blue and white porcelain,

160
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:38,680
I am the best in Jingdezhen.

161
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:40,360
Even looking across the whole country,

162
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:41,360
I have few rivals.

163
00:09:42,320 --> 00:09:43,360
I know Jingdezhen

164
00:09:43,360 --> 00:09:44,680
has always been full of hidden talents.

165
00:09:44,680 --> 00:09:45,440
Of course.

166
00:09:46,480 --> 00:09:48,640
Picking blue and white porcelain fragments,

167
00:09:48,640 --> 00:09:50,700
the most important thing is one word:

168
00:09:50,880 --> 00:09:51,480
destiny.

169
00:09:51,920 --> 00:09:53,380
You came to my little shop,

170
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:55,000
looked at these fragments,

171
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:56,400
and picked this one.

172
00:09:56,680 --> 00:09:57,940
It was unintentional,

173
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:00,600
but it's all destined.

174
00:10:01,120 --> 00:10:01,980
Let me tell you,

175
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:03,240
these fragments

176
00:10:03,600 --> 00:10:05,930
can be said to have their destined owners.

177
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:07,680
The one you hold,

178
00:10:07,800 --> 00:10:08,560
its owner

179
00:10:09,120 --> 00:10:09,920
is you.

180
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:16,600
I still don't quite understand what you mean.

181
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:18,480
But this piece is really pretty.

182
00:10:18,480 --> 00:10:19,810
How is it? Do you like it?

183
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:20,960
Boss,

184
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:22,640
how much are you selling it for?

185
00:10:22,640 --> 00:10:23,920
If it were anyone else,

186
00:10:24,520 --> 00:10:25,560
without a thousand yuan,

187
00:10:25,560 --> 00:10:27,040
they definitely couldn't take it.

188
00:10:27,040 --> 00:10:27,680
But

189
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:29,440
since you two have such destiny,

190
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:30,520
and you are a student,

191
00:10:30,520 --> 00:10:31,680
I'll give you a student price:

192
00:10:31,680 --> 00:10:32,360
nine hundred and fifty.

193
00:10:32,360 --> 00:10:32,890
Alright?

194
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:37,060
It's still too expensive.

195
00:10:40,560 --> 00:10:41,040
Miss.

196
00:10:41,200 --> 00:10:41,860
Miss. Miss.

197
00:10:42,240 --> 00:10:43,760
Wait a minute. Wait a minute.

198
00:10:43,760 --> 00:10:45,820
Since we have such a deep connection,

199
00:10:46,880 --> 00:10:48,160
how much can you offer?

200
00:10:49,040 --> 00:10:49,770
Two hundred.

201
00:10:55,160 --> 00:10:55,680
Miss.

202
00:10:57,120 --> 00:10:57,980
Three hundred.

203
00:10:58,720 --> 00:11:00,160
Deal. Thank you, boss.

204
00:11:05,600 --> 00:11:06,680
Boss, I've transferred the money to you.

205
00:11:06,680 --> 00:11:07,400
Okay. Good.

206
00:11:07,800 --> 00:11:08,400
Of course,

207
00:11:08,560 --> 00:11:09,520
I also hope

208
00:11:09,760 --> 00:11:11,000
young people like you

209
00:11:11,160 --> 00:11:12,520
can help us more

210
00:11:12,920 --> 00:11:14,320
to promote and publicize

211
00:11:14,520 --> 00:11:15,920
our Chinese ceramics.

212
00:11:16,520 --> 00:11:17,450
Thank you, boss.

213
00:11:18,040 --> 00:11:20,640
Otherwise I couldn't explain it to my teacher.

214
00:11:21,520 --> 00:11:22,120
Miss,

215
00:11:22,560 --> 00:11:23,760
where do you go to school?

216
00:11:23,760 --> 00:11:25,960
I'm at Jingdezhen Ceramic University.

217
00:11:26,280 --> 00:11:27,000
What major?

218
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:30,280
Freshman, major in cultural relic conservation.

219
00:11:31,640 --> 00:11:32,200
Well,

220
00:11:33,280 --> 00:11:35,040
is Yue Qixin your teacher?

221
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:36,560
Yes.

222
00:11:36,880 --> 00:11:38,080
Boss, do you know him?

223
00:11:40,520 --> 00:11:41,240
Sort of.

224
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:51,120
Boss, then,

225
00:11:51,520 --> 00:11:52,580
I'll get going now.

226
00:11:53,760 --> 00:11:54,200
Okay.

227
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:55,160
Take care.

228
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:56,840
Okay.

229
00:11:58,200 --> 00:11:58,680
Miss.

230
00:12:03,840 --> 00:12:04,440
Well,

231
00:12:05,160 --> 00:12:06,720
come visit often.

232
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:08,560
Come often.

233
00:12:08,560 --> 00:12:09,160
Goodbye.

234
00:12:09,640 --> 00:12:10,170
Goodbye.

235
00:12:25,200 --> 00:12:26,560
Let me help you take a look

236
00:12:26,560 --> 00:12:27,560
at your choices.

237
00:12:27,560 --> 00:12:28,280
Okay.

238
00:12:29,120 --> 00:12:31,200
Don't cry if you picked a fake.

239
00:12:32,760 --> 00:12:33,800
Mine can't be fake.

240
00:12:33,800 --> 00:12:34,440
Sir, look,

241
00:12:34,800 --> 00:12:36,040
the boss said it's Qing Famille Rose.

242
00:12:36,040 --> 00:12:36,800
What do you think?

243
00:12:36,800 --> 00:12:37,520
What do you mean 'he said'?

244
00:12:37,520 --> 00:12:38,040
What did you buy?

245
00:12:38,040 --> 00:12:39,280
Can't you tell?

246
00:12:39,760 --> 00:12:42,560
A blue and white porcelain piece from the Qianlong period.

247
00:12:42,560 --> 00:12:43,160
Let me see.

248
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:45,440
Sir, can you look at mine?

249
00:12:47,560 --> 00:12:49,680
The painting and details are very refined.

250
00:12:49,680 --> 00:12:50,200
Not bad.

251
00:12:50,640 --> 00:12:52,320
It should be blue and white porcelain from the Qianlong period.

252
00:12:52,320 --> 00:12:53,800
You met a good seller.

253
00:12:55,040 --> 00:12:55,840
Okay, thank you, sir.

254
00:12:55,840 --> 00:12:56,320
Wait a minute.

255
00:12:56,320 --> 00:12:57,000
Compare it

256
00:12:57,600 --> 00:12:59,240
and see where the difference is.

257
00:12:59,240 --> 00:12:59,840
All right.

258
00:13:05,680 --> 00:13:06,740
Qing Famille Rose.

259
00:13:07,960 --> 00:13:09,240
Very pretty. Not bad.

260
00:13:09,400 --> 00:13:10,260
Thank you, sir.

261
00:13:11,800 --> 00:13:13,000
Mr. Yue, look at mine.

262
00:13:13,120 --> 00:13:13,720
Let me see.

263
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:14,840
Yours

264
00:13:15,640 --> 00:13:16,700
is obviously fake.

265
00:13:16,800 --> 00:13:17,440
Fake?

266
00:13:18,080 --> 00:13:19,360
But the boss said it's Ru ware.

267
00:13:19,360 --> 00:13:20,120
Ru ware?

268
00:13:20,360 --> 00:13:21,440
If it were really Ru ware,

269
00:13:21,440 --> 00:13:22,680
you'd have made a fortune.

270
00:13:22,680 --> 00:13:24,000
I spent 300 yuan on it.

271
00:13:24,800 --> 00:13:26,000
Mr. Yue, 800 yuan.

272
00:13:26,080 --> 00:13:27,010
This one of yours

273
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:28,360
is worth 100 yuan.

274
00:13:28,440 --> 00:13:29,000
Take it.

275
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:30,680
Students,

276
00:13:31,280 --> 00:13:32,120
do you see this?

277
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:33,120
A lack of skill

278
00:13:33,480 --> 00:13:34,610
means losing money.

279
00:13:35,800 --> 00:13:36,800
This

280
00:13:37,720 --> 00:13:40,720
pine, bamboo, and plum pattern from the Qianlong era.

281
00:13:42,040 --> 00:13:42,520
Wait.

282
00:13:46,440 --> 00:13:48,320
Even I was almost fooled.

283
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:49,530
This one of yours

284
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:50,760
is a fake.

285
00:13:52,280 --> 00:13:53,040
Nowadays,

286
00:13:53,280 --> 00:13:54,560
in the antique market,

287
00:13:54,800 --> 00:13:57,280
making a small profit with this high-quality imitation,

288
00:13:57,280 --> 00:13:58,680
there is only one person.

289
00:13:59,360 --> 00:13:59,800
Who?

290
00:13:59,800 --> 00:14:00,440
Students,

291
00:14:00,880 --> 00:14:02,560
discuss it among yourselves,

292
00:14:02,640 --> 00:14:04,280
look and compare.

293
00:14:04,560 --> 00:14:05,760
Learn from each other.

294
00:14:05,760 --> 00:14:07,760
The teacher already said it's fake.

295
00:14:09,680 --> 00:14:10,480
Throw it away.

296
00:14:12,120 --> 00:14:14,000
But I think it looks really nice.

297
00:14:14,280 --> 00:14:15,160
A fake is a fake.

298
00:14:34,800 --> 00:14:36,840
It's a really good imitation.

299
00:14:37,720 --> 00:14:38,720
Selling it for 300

300
00:14:38,840 --> 00:14:40,300
wasn't exactly a rip-off.

301
00:14:50,760 --> 00:14:51,890
Come home tomorrow.

302
00:14:52,160 --> 00:14:53,760
I have something to tell you.

303
00:15:01,360 --> 00:15:02,600
I don't want to go to class.

304
00:15:02,600 --> 00:15:03,400
Hurry up.

305
00:15:03,880 --> 00:15:07,240
You have all personally visited the antique market.

306
00:15:07,360 --> 00:15:08,680
You must have realized

307
00:15:08,840 --> 00:15:10,360
that authenticating ancient porcelain...

308
00:15:10,360 --> 00:15:11,090
First of all,

309
00:15:11,680 --> 00:15:12,800
you must know

310
00:15:13,480 --> 00:15:15,940
the origin of antique imitation porcelain.

311
00:15:16,200 --> 00:15:18,280
The first step for antique imitation porcelain

312
00:15:18,280 --> 00:15:19,320
is to take the ceramic ware

313
00:15:19,320 --> 00:15:20,380
Pass it over there.

314
00:15:20,560 --> 00:15:24,040
and draw classic decorative patterns on it.

315
00:15:24,320 --> 00:15:25,000
Today,

316
00:15:25,160 --> 00:15:27,800
I'm handing out these plain ceramic bodies to you.

317
00:15:27,800 --> 00:15:29,360
I want you students

318
00:15:30,000 --> 00:15:31,400
to draw on these plain bodies

319
00:15:31,400 --> 00:15:32,400
using colors

320
00:15:32,720 --> 00:15:35,650
to create imitation Yuan blue-and-white patterns.

321
00:15:35,800 --> 00:15:36,840
Pay attention, everyone.

322
00:15:36,840 --> 00:15:40,200
It must be imitation Yuan blue-and-white patterns.

323
00:15:40,360 --> 00:15:42,520
Hand them back to me after you finish drawing.

324
00:15:42,520 --> 00:15:43,080
I will

325
00:15:43,200 --> 00:15:45,560
put them in the electric kiln for firing,

326
00:15:46,640 --> 00:15:48,170
and then return them to you.

327
00:15:48,480 --> 00:15:50,560
I will grade your work.

328
00:15:50,560 --> 00:15:51,400
Do you understand?

329
00:15:51,400 --> 00:15:52,440
Understood.

330
00:16:48,840 --> 00:16:50,880
I went to the old house today and cleaned it up.

331
00:16:50,880 --> 00:16:51,720
Take a look at these.

332
00:16:51,720 --> 00:16:53,520
Is there anything else you want?

333
00:17:22,599 --> 00:17:25,400
You still care so much about that person's things.

334
00:17:25,680 --> 00:17:27,339
Do you think he will come back?

335
00:17:27,400 --> 00:17:27,880
I don't.

336
00:17:33,360 --> 00:17:35,360
Then why did you choose this major?

337
00:17:36,280 --> 00:17:37,440
Do you think our family

338
00:17:37,440 --> 00:17:38,400
hasn't suffered enough

339
00:17:38,400 --> 00:17:39,440
from this?

340
00:17:44,840 --> 00:17:45,840
For so many years,

341
00:17:46,520 --> 00:17:48,180
he hasn't come back to see you.

342
00:17:48,680 --> 00:17:50,280
Do you really not resent him?

343
00:18:56,280 --> 00:18:57,160
Yuexin.

344
00:18:58,520 --> 00:18:59,240
Xiaocen.

345
00:19:02,160 --> 00:19:02,760
Xiaocen.

346
00:19:02,800 --> 00:19:05,330
I didn't expect you to like claw machines too.

347
00:19:05,360 --> 00:19:06,840
When I go to the mall,

348
00:19:06,840 --> 00:19:07,880
I come here to play.

349
00:19:07,880 --> 00:19:08,480
Really?

350
00:19:08,480 --> 00:19:09,160
That's great.

351
00:19:09,160 --> 00:19:10,640
We can come together next time.

352
00:19:10,640 --> 00:19:11,040
Okay.

353
00:19:11,040 --> 00:19:12,120
Because Wu Jing and Yan Xue

354
00:19:12,120 --> 00:19:13,380
refuse to come with me.

355
00:19:13,520 --> 00:19:15,180
They think it's too childish.

356
00:19:16,960 --> 00:19:17,520
Xiaocen,

357
00:19:18,000 --> 00:19:19,860
why did you only get so few tokens?

358
00:19:20,160 --> 00:19:22,420
I just bought a few to satisfy my craving.

359
00:19:22,640 --> 00:19:23,900
How can that be enough?

360
00:19:24,400 --> 00:19:25,680
I'll share some with you.

361
00:19:25,680 --> 00:19:26,440
No, thanks.

362
00:19:27,080 --> 00:19:28,120
Coin inserted successfully.

363
00:19:28,120 --> 00:19:29,380
Please start the game.

364
00:19:36,200 --> 00:19:36,800
Let's get this one.

365
00:19:36,800 --> 00:19:37,280
Okay.

366
00:19:39,280 --> 00:19:39,840
Come on.

367
00:19:43,680 --> 00:19:44,520
Awesome!

368
00:19:44,640 --> 00:19:45,520
Awesome!

369
00:19:46,240 --> 00:19:47,840
Want to try again?

370
00:19:52,360 --> 00:19:53,800
Why don't we go somewhere else?

371
00:19:53,800 --> 00:19:54,360
Okay.

372
00:19:57,560 --> 00:19:58,480
Coin inserted successfully.

373
00:19:58,480 --> 00:19:59,920
Please hurry up.

374
00:20:02,080 --> 00:20:03,400
So close!

375
00:20:06,480 --> 00:20:07,940
How are you so good at this?

376
00:20:08,160 --> 00:20:09,420
Do you have any tricks?

377
00:20:09,560 --> 00:20:10,640
Maybe it's just luck.

378
00:20:10,640 --> 00:20:12,400
Some people can never catch anything.

379
00:20:12,400 --> 00:20:14,400
But others get it on their first try.

380
00:20:19,560 --> 00:20:20,620
Let's keep trying.

381
00:20:25,440 --> 00:20:26,240
What's wrong?

382
00:20:30,680 --> 00:20:32,800
It's not about luck at all.

383
00:20:33,560 --> 00:20:34,800
There's a trick to it.

384
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:36,600
She is taking advantage of you.

385
00:20:36,600 --> 00:20:37,660
Taking advantage?

386
00:20:39,040 --> 00:20:41,400
Actually, there's a strategy to the claw machine.

387
00:20:41,400 --> 00:20:42,260
What strategy?

388
00:20:43,000 --> 00:20:44,080
Generally speaking,

389
00:20:44,080 --> 00:20:46,000
for the first seven or eight tries,

390
00:20:46,000 --> 00:20:47,260
the claw is very loose,

391
00:20:47,400 --> 00:20:48,960
so the chance of winning is very low.

392
00:20:48,960 --> 00:20:50,120
Then there will be one or two times

393
00:20:50,120 --> 00:20:51,640
when the claw is very tight.

394
00:20:51,640 --> 00:20:54,100
That's when the chances of winning are high.

395
00:20:54,600 --> 00:20:55,320
That girl,

396
00:20:55,320 --> 00:20:57,760
she waits for you to fail before she tries,

397
00:20:57,880 --> 00:20:59,840
so it's very easy for her to catch one.

398
00:20:59,840 --> 00:21:01,160
How do you know so much?

399
00:21:01,320 --> 00:21:03,920
Because I often stake out others like that too.

400
00:21:04,120 --> 00:21:05,240
Really?

401
00:21:06,800 --> 00:21:07,280
Also,

402
00:21:07,560 --> 00:21:09,800
you can wait until the staff restocks.

403
00:21:09,960 --> 00:21:11,520
They'll put the dolls on the edge,

404
00:21:11,520 --> 00:21:13,380
which makes them easier to catch.

405
00:21:13,400 --> 00:21:15,040
Also, when catching a doll, don't grab the head.

406
00:21:15,040 --> 00:21:15,840
Grab its body,

407
00:21:15,840 --> 00:21:16,970
it'll hold tighter.

408
00:21:20,360 --> 00:21:22,290
Why are you looking at me like that?

409
00:21:24,000 --> 00:21:25,240
You know what, Xiaocen?

410
00:21:25,240 --> 00:21:26,560
Since the beginning of the semester,

411
00:21:26,560 --> 00:21:27,800
everything you've said to me

412
00:21:27,800 --> 00:21:28,520
combined isn't as much as

413
00:21:28,520 --> 00:21:29,640
what you just said.

414
00:21:31,800 --> 00:21:32,440
I'm sorry.

415
00:21:32,440 --> 00:21:34,400
Did I talk too much just now?

416
00:21:34,400 --> 00:21:35,240
Did I annoy you?

417
00:21:35,240 --> 00:21:36,280
Don't be sorry.

418
00:21:36,400 --> 00:21:37,440
You were very cute just now.

419
00:21:37,440 --> 00:21:38,240
I really like it.

420
00:21:38,240 --> 00:21:39,370
Talk more next time.

421
00:21:39,560 --> 00:21:40,760
Thank you, Yuexin.

422
00:21:40,960 --> 00:21:41,890
You're welcome.

423
00:21:51,480 --> 00:21:52,140
Here you go.

424
00:21:53,880 --> 00:21:54,320
One more time.

425
00:21:54,320 --> 00:21:56,980
Hello, what can I exchange these four dolls for?

426
00:21:57,360 --> 00:21:58,520
Four dolls

427
00:21:59,440 --> 00:22:00,900
can get you this keychain.

428
00:22:03,880 --> 00:22:05,320
Hello, I'm a member.

429
00:22:05,440 --> 00:22:06,280
Can you check

430
00:22:06,280 --> 00:22:07,520
what the points I saved here before

431
00:22:07,520 --> 00:22:09,920
plus these four dolls can be exchanged for?

432
00:22:10,120 --> 00:22:11,080
This big doll.

433
00:22:13,600 --> 00:22:14,480
I'll take this one.

434
00:22:14,480 --> 00:22:14,810
Okay.

435
00:22:16,680 --> 00:22:18,080
Xiaocen, this is for you.

436
00:22:19,240 --> 00:22:19,960
No need.

437
00:22:19,960 --> 00:22:22,000
Most of these dolls were caught by you.

438
00:22:22,000 --> 00:22:23,520
I can't even fit them on my bed.

439
00:22:23,520 --> 00:22:24,720
Since you can't bring them back to the dorm,

440
00:22:24,720 --> 00:22:26,120
you should take them back.

441
00:22:26,120 --> 00:22:27,120
Thank you, Yuexin.

442
00:22:27,120 --> 00:22:28,050
You're welcome.

443
00:22:32,400 --> 00:22:33,840
Can you hurry up?

444
00:22:33,840 --> 00:22:36,170
You've been looking at it for half an hour.

445
00:22:38,840 --> 00:22:39,600
You're back.

446
00:22:40,160 --> 00:22:43,000
Sister, you're finally back.

447
00:22:43,320 --> 00:22:44,600
Sister, what did you bring?

448
00:22:44,600 --> 00:22:45,530
A little rabbit.

449
00:22:46,240 --> 00:22:47,360
What are you holding?

450
00:22:47,360 --> 00:22:49,020
I caught it with my classmate.

451
00:22:49,120 --> 00:22:51,000
Sister, isn't this for me?

452
00:22:51,000 --> 00:22:52,400
How could it be for you?

453
00:22:52,400 --> 00:22:54,130
You two, come here and sit down.

454
00:23:00,640 --> 00:23:01,640
Who gave it to you?

455
00:23:02,000 --> 00:23:03,360
A boy or a girl?

456
00:23:04,160 --> 00:23:05,840
Mom, a girl.

457
00:23:05,960 --> 00:23:06,760
I'll show you.

458
00:23:07,160 --> 00:23:08,600
She's our class monitor.

459
00:23:08,960 --> 00:23:11,420
We went to play the claw machine after class.

460
00:23:12,800 --> 00:23:15,240
You're getting along well with your classmates now.

461
00:23:15,240 --> 00:23:15,970
That's good.

462
00:23:17,080 --> 00:23:19,680
Why are you looking at me? Look at the question.

463
00:23:21,480 --> 00:23:24,840
No, I'm too tired, Auntie.

464
00:23:25,840 --> 00:23:27,970
How about we go pick up my mom from work?

465
00:23:28,040 --> 00:23:28,600
Sit down.

466
00:23:33,480 --> 00:23:36,010
You have an excuse for everything, don't you?

467
00:23:36,760 --> 00:23:38,480
I've never seen you so dutiful.

468
00:23:38,480 --> 00:23:39,240
You just want to slack off.

469
00:23:39,240 --> 00:23:40,680
My sister is back.

470
00:23:40,680 --> 00:23:42,960
Aunt, go tutor her.

471
00:23:43,160 --> 00:23:44,560
My eyes hurt.

472
00:23:44,560 --> 00:23:46,200
I'll lie down for a bit.

473
00:23:46,600 --> 00:23:47,800
Get up, get up, get up.

474
00:23:47,960 --> 00:23:48,760
Sit properly.

475
00:23:49,160 --> 00:23:51,200
Your mom spoils you, but I won't.

476
00:23:51,320 --> 00:23:52,960
Do you know how competitive it is now?

477
00:23:52,960 --> 00:23:54,040
If you don't study hard now,

478
00:23:54,040 --> 00:23:55,680
how can you get into a good school when you grow up?

479
00:23:55,680 --> 00:23:56,610
Ask your sister.

480
00:23:57,040 --> 00:23:58,840
Hasn't she been through this since she was little?

481
00:23:58,840 --> 00:23:59,280
Yes.

482
00:24:00,120 --> 00:24:00,680
Right?

483
00:24:00,760 --> 00:24:01,160
Yes.

484
00:24:02,680 --> 00:24:03,680
Did you hear that?

485
00:24:06,200 --> 00:24:09,040
You must finish this set of questions today.

486
00:24:14,800 --> 00:24:15,680
Well,

487
00:24:16,400 --> 00:24:18,000
can I be excused now?

488
00:24:20,560 --> 00:24:21,320
Go.

489
00:24:23,800 --> 00:24:25,660
I'll cut some fruit for you later.

490
00:24:28,840 --> 00:24:31,480
There's definitely something going on between them.

491
00:24:31,480 --> 00:24:32,400
I think,

492
00:24:32,800 --> 00:24:34,460
at this point in the semester,

493
00:24:34,800 --> 00:24:37,360
things have already taken shape.

494
00:24:37,360 --> 00:24:40,200
Anyway, I don't think the boys in our class are good enough.

495
00:24:40,200 --> 00:24:41,360
It's not that they aren't good enough.

496
00:24:41,360 --> 00:24:42,280
I just feel

497
00:24:42,400 --> 00:24:43,520
that college romances are unreliable.

498
00:24:43,520 --> 00:24:44,480
Then who do you think,

499
00:24:44,480 --> 00:24:45,810
if we rank them by looks,

500
00:24:46,160 --> 00:24:47,400
among the boys in our class,

501
00:24:47,400 --> 00:24:48,800
is the most handsome?

502
00:24:49,000 --> 00:24:50,130
Don't you guys think

503
00:24:50,160 --> 00:24:51,880
Li Zhuoting is quite cute?

504
00:24:54,720 --> 00:24:56,080
Are you serious?

505
00:24:56,200 --> 00:24:57,360
Are you okay?

506
00:24:58,240 --> 00:25:00,400
He follows Wang Lin around every day.

507
00:25:01,000 --> 00:25:01,520
Wang Lin?

508
00:25:01,520 --> 00:25:03,450
Forget it. Don't mention Wang Lin.

509
00:25:03,480 --> 00:25:05,360
Those two are birds of a feather.

510
00:25:06,080 --> 00:25:07,400
But don't you think

511
00:25:07,560 --> 00:25:09,400
his smile is very shy?

512
00:25:09,680 --> 00:25:11,000
Are you okay?

513
00:25:11,400 --> 00:25:12,400
If we rank them by looks,

514
00:25:12,400 --> 00:25:14,120
Xu Xiao is definitely ahead of them.

515
00:25:14,120 --> 00:25:15,000
Exactly.

516
00:25:15,120 --> 00:25:16,640
But Xu Xiao and Zhao Xiaocen,

517
00:25:16,640 --> 00:25:18,400
they go to class together every day.

518
00:25:18,400 --> 00:25:19,000
Yeah.

519
00:25:19,240 --> 00:25:20,480
I've seen them after school several times,

520
00:25:20,480 --> 00:25:21,440
and they always leave together.

521
00:25:21,440 --> 00:25:23,080
So is there something going on between them or not?

522
00:25:23,080 --> 00:25:23,800
I think there is.

523
00:25:23,800 --> 00:25:24,720
Definitely.

524
00:25:25,040 --> 00:25:26,900
Then isn't that unfair to Yuexin?

525
00:25:27,080 --> 00:25:28,280
If we're talking about who came first,

526
00:25:28,280 --> 00:25:29,480
Yuexin should be ahead.

527
00:25:29,480 --> 00:25:29,840
I...

528
00:25:29,840 --> 00:25:30,720
Exactly.

529
00:25:30,960 --> 00:25:31,520
This...

530
00:25:31,520 --> 00:25:32,240
What are you doing?

531
00:25:32,240 --> 00:25:33,480
Don't deny it.

532
00:25:33,640 --> 00:25:34,720
During military training,

533
00:25:34,720 --> 00:25:36,160
didn't we already interrogate it out of you?

534
00:25:36,160 --> 00:25:37,000
Right.

535
00:25:37,000 --> 00:25:37,400
No.

536
00:25:37,400 --> 00:25:38,280
You just have a crush on Xu Xiao.

537
00:25:38,280 --> 00:25:39,000
No,

538
00:25:39,000 --> 00:25:40,360
you guys forced me to say that.

539
00:25:40,360 --> 00:25:40,960
I don't.

540
00:25:41,000 --> 00:25:41,640
Did you ask?

541
00:25:41,640 --> 00:25:42,360
I didn't.

542
00:25:42,360 --> 00:25:43,200
Neither did I.

543
00:25:43,560 --> 00:25:44,040
Wait.

544
00:25:44,680 --> 00:25:45,240
Yuexin,

545
00:25:45,600 --> 00:25:47,200
do you still like Xu Xiao now?

546
00:25:48,280 --> 00:25:48,920
Don't ask that.

547
00:25:48,920 --> 00:25:51,180
You have feelings for him, just admit it.

548
00:25:51,320 --> 00:25:53,000
If they're not together,

549
00:25:53,440 --> 00:25:54,640
would you make a move?

550
00:25:57,840 --> 00:25:59,400
It's getting late.

551
00:25:59,440 --> 00:26:00,640
Should we go to sleep?

552
00:26:00,760 --> 00:26:01,160
Good night.

553
00:26:01,160 --> 00:26:02,440
Yuexin, you're doing it again.

554
00:26:02,440 --> 00:26:03,440
You're doing it again.

555
00:26:03,440 --> 00:26:04,760
Always running away.

556
00:26:04,760 --> 00:26:05,640
You never admit it.

557
00:26:05,640 --> 00:26:06,240
Exactly.

558
00:26:06,240 --> 00:26:07,570
What's so hard to admit?

559
00:26:07,920 --> 00:26:11,960
Listen, the bugle of the new journey sounds.

560
00:26:12,000 --> 00:26:16,080
Listen, the bugle of the new journey sounds.

561
00:26:16,480 --> 00:26:19,920
The goal of a strong military calls ahead.

562
00:26:20,200 --> 00:26:23,920
The goal of a strong military calls ahead.

563
00:26:43,040 --> 00:26:44,600
Don't forget the whole class is going tonight.

564
00:26:44,600 --> 00:26:45,560
Okay.

565
00:26:45,560 --> 00:26:46,080
Got it.

566
00:26:47,640 --> 00:26:49,560
Let's buy some food first. I'm a bit hungry.

567
00:26:49,560 --> 00:26:51,290
Is Xiaocen going to this party?

568
00:26:51,480 --> 00:26:52,210
I don't know.

569
00:26:53,920 --> 00:26:54,480
Xiaocen,

570
00:26:55,240 --> 00:26:56,900
we are having a party tonight.

571
00:26:57,080 --> 00:26:58,560
Yuexin is a good girl.

572
00:26:59,240 --> 00:27:00,920
I was too passive before.
